# Volo Design System

## Colors — ONLY volo-* tokens

Never use raw Tailwind colors (red-600, emerald-600, sky-400, zinc-*, etc.) in component or page code.
Use exclusively:

- `volo-accent` / `volo-accent-hover` / `volo-accent-light` — CTA, active states, highlights
- `volo-text` / `volo-muted` — primary and secondary text
- `volo-bg` / `volo-surface` — backgrounds
- `volo-border` — borders and dividers
- `volo-success` / `volo-error` — status indicators only
- `volo-info` — informational accents (links, secondary interactive)

## Typography Scale

| Role | Classes |
|------|---------|
| Hero heading | `text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold tracking-tight` |
| Section heading | `text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-heading font-bold` |
| Card heading | `text-lg font-heading font-semibold` |
| Body | `text-base leading-relaxed` |
| Caption / meta | `text-sm text-volo-muted` |
| Price (large) | `text-2xl font-heading font-bold` with unit in `text-sm text-volo-muted ml-1` |
| Price (compact) | `text-lg font-heading font-bold` |

Always format prices with `new Intl.NumberFormat('pl-PL').format(amount)` and separate the unit (PLN / os., PLN / przejazd) visually.

## Hero Sections

MANDATORY: background photo with overlay gradient. Never use bare CSS gradients without an image.

```tsx
<section className="relative min-h-[480px] lg:min-h-[560px] flex items-center">
  <img src={imageUrl} alt="..." className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
  <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/70 via-black/40 to-transparent" />
  <div className="relative z-10 section-padding container-wide">
    {/* Light text on dark overlay */}
  </div>
</section>
```

Hero text is always white/light on the photo overlay. CTA button uses `btn-primary`.

## Cards — Three Depth Levels

- `.card` — default: subtle border + shadow-sm (for lists, secondary content)
- `.card-elevated` — stronger shadow, slight scale on hover (for SKU cards, booking summary)
- `.card-prominent` — accent border-left or top, heavier shadow (for buyout option, featured items)

## CTA Hierarchy

- ONE `btn-primary` per visible screen area
- Trust hint near CTA: small text like "Bezpłatna anulacja do 48h" or "Bezpieczna płatność" in `text-sm text-volo-muted` directly below the button
- Secondary actions use `btn-secondary` or `btn-ghost`

## Micro-interactions

- All transitions: `duration-200 ease-out`
- Use `motion-safe:` prefix for transforms and opacity animations
- Hover on cards: `motion-safe:hover:shadow-lg motion-safe:hover:-translate-y-0.5`
- Step transitions in forms: simple opacity/position, not instant re-render
- Disabled buttons: `disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:hover:shadow-none`

## Image Placeholders

When images fail to load, show warm gradient `bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-100 to-orange-50` instead of cold zinc/gray.
